trans-unit.source: For more information about the `ITypeComp` interface, see the MSDN Library.
Maps a name to a member of a type, or binds global variables and functions contained in a type library.
For more information, please see the existing documentation for `ITypeComp::Bind` in the MSDN library.
A hash value for `szName` computed by <xref uid="langword_csharp_LHashValOfNameSys" name="LHashValOfNameSys" href=""></xref>.
A flags word containing one or more of the invoke flags defined in the <xref uid="langword_csharp_INVOKEKIND" name="INVOKEKIND" href=""></xref> enumeration.

On successful return, a reference to the type description that contains the item to which it is bound, if a <xref uid="langword_csharp_FUNCDESC" name="FUNCDESC" href=""></xref> or <xref uid="langword_csharp_VARDESC" name="VARDESC" href=""></xref> was returned.

A reference to a <xref uid="langword_csharp_DESCKIND" name="DESCKIND" href=""></xref> enumerator that indicates whether the name bound to is a <xref uid="langword_csharp_VARDESC" name="VARDESC" href=""></xref>, <xref uid="langword_csharp_FUNCDESC" name="FUNCDESC" href=""></xref>, or <xref uid="langword_csharp_TYPECOMP" name="TYPECOMP" href=""></xref>.

A reference to the bound-to <xref uid="langword_csharp_VARDESC" name="VARDESC" href=""></xref>, <xref uid="langword_csharp_FUNCDESC" name="FUNCDESC" href=""></xref>, or <xref uid="langword_csharp_ITypeComp" name="ITypeComp" href=""></xref> interface.
Binds to the type descriptions contained within a type library.
For more information, please see the existing documentation for `ITypeComp::BindType` in the MSDN library.
A hash value for `szName` determined by <xref uid="langword_csharp_LHashValOfNameSys" name="LHashValOfNameSys" href=""></xref>.
On successful return, a reference to an <xref uid="langword_csharp_ITypeInfo" name="ITypeInfo" href=""></xref> of the type to which `szName` was bound.
On successful return, a reference to an <xref uid="langword_csharp_ITypeComp" name="ITypeComp" href=""></xref> variable.
